      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Workflow note: cache hits short-circuit to citation formatting; vague prompts loop through clarification; low evidence routes to an honest fallback instead of unsupported generation.",
