      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Production selection: the backend uses Qdrant Cloud when QDRANT_CLIENT_API_ENDPOINT and QDRANT_CLIENT_API_KEY are set; otherwise it falls back to local Qdrant host/port.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 40
